---
import moreinfo1 from "../assets/moreinfo-1.jpg";
import moreinfo2 from "../assets/moreinfo-2.jpg";
import moreinfo3 from "../assets/moreinfo-3.jpg";
---

<section id="moreinfo" class="extension-section">
  <h2 class="title">延伸資訊</h2>
  <p class="subtitle">從書本認識更多新莊與產業轉型</p>

  <div class="cards">
    
    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="card">
      <img src={moreinfo1.src} alt="新莊騷 issue08" class="cover" />

      <h3 class="book-title">新莊騷 issue08<br/>新新莊人的新生活–島內移居</h3>
      <p class="description">
        從人口增長到城市變化、巷街區的轉型<br>
        中正路大型工廠的記憶地圖<br>
        新生代職人的創業理念與職涯發展
      </p>

      <a href="https://reurl.cc/1kvrVV" target="_blank" class="more-btn">了解更多</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="card">
      <img src={moreinfo2.src} alt="新莊騷 issue01" class="cover" />

      <h3 class="book-title">新莊騷 issue01<br/>咖啡覺醒力</h3>
      <p class="description">
        訪談港澳、15 位新莊獨具風格的咖啡師專訪<br>
        咖啡文化與生活體驗的合而為一<br>
        現代版格格巷下、與人交流的咖啡店
      </p>

      <a href="https://reurl.cc/eVzjKx" target="_blank" class="more-btn">了解更多</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="card">
      <img src={moreinfo3.src} alt="創新的10個原點" class="cover" />

      <h3 class="book-title">創新的10個原點<br/>拆解 2000 家企業顛覆產業規則的創新思維</h3>
      <p class="description">
        突破盲點、建立路徑門檻、資源重組<br>
        112 種創新策略應用：失敗不是因為你想得太小<br>
        解析 Google、星巴克、Apple 等創新典範
      </p>

      <a href="https://reurl.cc/MMOnQk" target="_blank" class="more-btn">了解更多</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .extension-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    color: #4a3423; /* 類似簡報的咖啡色字體 */
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .card {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .cover {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .book-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .more-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 9999px; /* 圓角按鈕 */
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid #333;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .more-btn:hover {
    background: #333;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  /* RWD：手機改單欄 */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .extension-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
